mod_Firewall = Module for controling iptables | Threaded
mod_Spamhaus = Module for getting "blacklist" from spamhaus
mod_Dshield  = Module for getting "blacklist" from dshield
mod_CLI      = Module for reading userinput from the Console | Threaded

mod_Passive  = Templatemodule with optional event timer | without threading
mod_Active   = Templatemodule with threading and FiFo for input

To activate one or more modules, copy them into the root-dir.
Create an entry in ./config/bird.conf | modules = module_name

ATTN:
Please load primary modules first (like mod_Firewall, mod_Dshield).
